<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA67">
<l>pāmpu matiyu maṭamāṉum pāypuliyun</l>
<l>tāmpayiṉṟu tāḻaruvi tūṅkutalā - lāmpoṉ</l>
<l>ṉuruvaṭivi lōṅkoḷicēr kaṇṇutalāṉ kōlat</l>
<l>tiruvaṭiyiṉ mēya cilampu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is because the snake, the moon, the youthfull stag and the leaping tiger</l>
<l>are accustomed [to it and] because the waterfall hangs there, the mountain slope</l>
<l>that where dwells by the beautiful sacred foot of the one with a forehead with a high</l>
<l>bright eye in the form the colour of gold.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
